{"tid":1684160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[可行性研究] 有無可能開發「公投黃店」","createTime":"2019-10-31T03:11:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T05:11:38.000Z","uid":20693,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6f0179fa29764793d59a4141b95323c5df85fbc0","tid":1684160,"uid":20693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:11:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SQy92Qe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSQy92Qe.jpg&h=a128d379&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n大部分香港人甚至黃絲們都可能未感受到公投既好處<br />\n但既然我地乜都唔多但錢多，其實有無可能眾籌買個舖, 玩模擬管治?<br />\n合眾人之力買舖--&gt;公投--&gt;又可以請返被拉的義士--&gt;齊齊率先享受民主制度<br />\n呢個版本我覺得易入口, 但我無營商經驗又唔熟法律, 有無巴絲幫幫手睇下可唔可行? 有錯請屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61f97f5fd259021ce0347efa255c1050036684a7","tid":1684160,"uid":20693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:12:50.000Z","msg":"開始倒數<br />\n10"},{"pid":"10f6f8beb52eb0449533e8adc97e7186e0d0f4ee","tid":1684160,"uid":20693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:14:09.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"7b8b04aeb8a5b28b30d090c72d2f1e15fa4d9e8d","tid":1684160,"uid":20693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:16:00.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"a6b192e2f2a19781eaf6b26ea2a3d6c69c2d473e","tid":1684160,"uid":20693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:16:58.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"918aa2d0b9bd252b1e40a32d04c2fe246a4928ab","tid":1684160,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:17:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"18c850e834b8db2d5fff933d02f18adee415c805","tid":1684160,"uid":20693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:18:47.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"65f765652bcb3d0c4bf64add64d248e9066dc9c1","tid":1684160,"uid":20693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:20:55.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"9773a837148e6300679